sentence: Her opponent, Harriet Hageman, who has drawn the vociferous support of Mr. Trump and his family, raised $443,000 last quarter and has about $380,000 cash on hand.
title: Republicans Who Voted to Impeach Trump Out-Raised Primary Rivals

sentence: One of the starkest examples comes out of Wyoming, where Rep. Liz Cheney raised $2 million in the fourth quarter of 2021more than quadrupling the cash haul of her Trump-backed opponent, Harriet Hageman, who brought in $443,000, according to Axios.
title: Liz Cheney and other Trump targets trounce his endorsees in the fundraising race
